James ZEBRANKE, Jr., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4512 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The mandate in 2D13-6074 having issued March 17, 2016, this petition alleging ineffective assistance of appellate counsel is dismissed as untimely. See Fla. R. App. P. 9.141(d)(5).

CASANUEVA, LUCAS, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
